staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100014: Oh! Well this is a little disappointing...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100015: I had hoped he'd come and do it himself...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100016: Oh! But maybe that was a bit rude of me.
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100017: I didn't mean to suggest I wasn't thankful!
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100018: Just disappointed. In the circumstances. Not in you.
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100019: I suppose I should give you some kind of reward?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100020: Maybe that will be of some use to you?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100022: I want to thank him too...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100024: How have you fared of late?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100025: ^c:1486b0;Oscar^c:pop; really does keep this place tidy...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100026: I wonder how he manages to find the time to clean an entire village of miscreants by himself?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100028: Why, I certainly cannot tell you that! We fey value our privacy!
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100029: Do I miss being coated in rubbish?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100030: Well... I did spend many a year that way...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100031: But no, of course not! I had even begun to forget the scent of flowers!
